query:
SELECT 
  i.id,
  i.invoiceNumber,
  i.status,
  i.pickingOrderId,
  po.customerOrderNumber,
  po.shippingStatus
FROM invoices i
LEFT JOIN pickingOrders po ON po.id = i.pickingOrderId
WHERE i.pickingOrderId IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY i.id DESC
LIMIT 10;
